data.description:
Welcome to the heart of a growing community in S. Bossier, where convenience meets comfort a& a sense of community prevails. Situated close to BAFB, this charming residence offers easy access to work, & amenities. Boasting 3 bedrooms downstairs & a bonus room and or bedroom upstairs with no closet, this home provides ample space for living, working, & entertaining. Whether you're seeking a quiet retreat or a space to gather with loved ones, the thoughtful layout accommodates your every need. Nestled in a quiet community, you'll enjoy the tranquility of your surroundings while still being close to everything. Take leisurely strolls through the neighborhood or enjoy peaceful evenings on your front porch, knowing that you're part of a friendly community.
Added was some new carpet, new water heater, fresh paint. And new tile in kitchen, secondary bathroom, hall and laundry room. *Property cannot go FHA due to flipping guidelines. OWNER AGENT
